$a2 = $a**2;
$b = random(1,9,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Solve the equation \( \displaystyle \frac{x}{$a x-$a2}- $b = \frac{1}{x-$a}\).
$BR $BR 
Does the equation have a solution? $BR
$BR
If so, enter the solution.  If there is no solution, enter "None".
$BR
\( x = \) \{ans_rule(20) \}
EOT

